# Release Workflows

- `publish-v5-beta.yml` must publish from `v5.x.x`, not an arbitrary event branch.
- `update-v5-docs.yml` uses `v5.x.x` as source and opens/updates a docs PR against `main`.
- Main-branch docs hooks call external docs systems; do not trigger or broaden them without approval.
- Keep secrets in GitHub Actions secrets and preserve least-privilege workflow permissions.
- Read `.agents/skills/release-workflows/` before changing release automation.
